sql:
SELECT page_id, COUNT(campaign_id) AS total_campaigns
FROM ad_campaigns
GROUP BY page_id;

SELECT platform, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT targeting_name) AS unique_targeting_values
FROM targeting_options
GROUP BY platform;

SELECT platform, SUM(active_ads) AS total_active_ads
FROM ads_in_library
GROUP BY platform;

external_knowledge:
- 'Beacon of activity' is a metaphor for the platform and page with the highest number of active campaigns;
- 'Shining the brightest' refers to the highest count of active campaigns;
- 'Active ad campaigns ablaze' metaphorically represents the campaigns that are in an 'active' status.

'Start of the year' refers to the January period, specifically '2022-01-01' to '2022-01-31';
'Ads' here denote advertisements run on the Facebook platform targeting a specific geographical location;
'A greater than zero spending' implies any campaign that had actual monetary investment.

sql:
SELECT platform, COUNT(*) AS num_pages
FROM pages
GROUP BY platform;

SELECT SUM(budget) AS total_budget
FROM ad_campaigns
WHERE client_id = 'client123';

SELECT active_ads
FROM ads_in_library
WHERE platform = 'Twitter';

SELECT *
FROM ad_campaigns
WHERE platform = 'Facebook' AND budget > (SELECT AVG(budget) FROM ad_campaigns);

SELECT campaign_name, ad_spend_to_date
FROM ad_campaigns
ORDER BY CAST(ad_spend_to_date AS REAL) DESC;

external_knowledge:
- "Sailing in the vast ocean of advertisements" refers to the various pages engaging in advertising campaigns; 
- "showcasing their banners with a clear purpose" indicates the objectives of the ad campaigns; 
- "under what flags" is a metaphor for the disclaimers associated with the ads; 
- "how big a wave have they created" symbolizes the total amount spent on ads; 
- "the size of their fleet" represents the number of ads each page has in its library.

sql:
SELECT targeting_value
FROM targeting_options
WHERE campaign_id = '0';

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT page_id) 
FROM ad_spend 
WHERE amount_spent > 100;

SELECT page_id, platform, spend_type, SUM(amount_spent) AS total_ad_spend
FROM ad_spend
GROUP BY page_id, platform, spend_type;
